items.title: Nathan James Piper Faux Marble Modern Contemporary Accent Side or Coffee Table for Living Room with Metal Frame, White/Black
items.description:
20"D x 39"W x 17"H
This rectangle white living room table is the perfect center piece to add sophistication and elegance to the room.
Abby is a sturdy coffee table thanks to a durable criss-cross construction with a gunmetal finish. Abby's metal leg frame showcases industrial lines to complement the luxurious aspect of the marble table top.
This coffee table is the perfect small space statement piece and has plenty of room to display books, your favorite flower bouquet, and decorative accessories.
The marble table is a functional 40 inch long modern piece perfect to display all of the beverage and snacks to entertain all your guests.
Easy 20-minute assembly.

Base: Steel
Frame Material: Metal
